00:23:57.710 --> 00:23:59.300
It's a stereograph card.

00:23:59.300 --> 00:24:04.870 position:61%
Stereographs are two nearly identical
images, mounted side by side on a card.

00:24:04.870 --> 00:24:08.370
When looked at through a special
viewer and you can see the woman

00:24:08.370 --> 00:24:12.620
