images of the new woman on stereograph cards.

00:24:51.910 --> 00:24:57.410 position:59%
A simple entertainment can have a much
deeper meaning if we delve into it.

00:24:57.410 --> 00:25:00.440 position:67%
It is, it's kind of like a view master toy.

